irssiFusion

irssiFusion is an Android application that gives you full functionaility of
your remote irssi session on your portable Android device.

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

This is the source code distribution of irssiFusion. If you are looking for a 
compiled 'ready to use' version (APK) it is not ready yet! Help develop!

irssiFusion will eventually be avaiable at the official Android market.

If you are a developer and want to contribute to irssiFusion, checkout
our repository at github:

 https://github.com/platinummonkey/irssi-Fusion

The application project is located in irssiFusion/ and the irssi script and
server script are located in ircTalk_server/ - You will need socket-remote.pl
and test_server.py.

Drop me a line for questions regarding irssiFusion or use one of the following
ressources:

IRC:           irc.freenode.net #irssifusion
Homepage:      coming soon

